@startuml uc5_list_part_2
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title UC-05 Part 2: Status-based Navigation và Actions

actor "Marketing\nAnalyst" as User
participant "Web UI\n(Next.js)" as UI
participant "Project Service\n(Golang)" as ProjectSvc
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Navigation Based on Status ==

User -> UI: Click Project card\n(or action button)
activate UI

UI -> UI: Check project.status

alt Status = "draft"
    UI -> UI: Show actions:\n- "Edit" (UC-01)\n- "Execute" (UC-03)\n- "Delete"

    User -> UI: Click "Execute"
    UI --> User: Navigate to UC-03\n(Execute & Monitor)

else Status = "process" (Running)
    UI -> UI: Show actions:\n- "View Progress" (UC-03)\n- Delete button DISABLED

    User -> UI: Click "View Progress"
    UI --> User: Navigate to UC-03\n(Monitor page)

else Status = "completed"
    UI -> UI: Show actions:\n- "View Results" (UC-04)\n- "Export Report" (UC-06)\n- "Delete"

    User -> UI: Click "View Results"
    UI --> User: Navigate to UC-04\n(Dashboard)

else Status = "failed"
    UI -> UI: Show actions:\n- "Retry" (UC-03)\n- "Delete"

    User -> UI: Click "Retry"
    UI --> User: Navigate to UC-03\n(with same config)
end

deactivate UI

== Soft Delete Project ==

User -> UI: Click "Delete" button\n(on Completed project)
activate UI

UI -> UI: Show confirmation dialog:\n"Delete project 'Brand A Analysis'?\nThis cannot be undone."

User -> UI: Click "Confirm"

UI -> ProjectSvc: DELETE /api/v1/projects/:id\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>
activate ProjectSvc

ProjectSvc -> ProjectSvc: Verify ownership:\nproject.created_by == user_id

ProjectSvc -> ProjectSvc: Check business rules:\n- Cannot delete if status = "process"

ProjectSvc -> DB: UPDATE projects\nSET deleted_at = NOW(),\n    updated_at = NOW()\nWHERE id = :id\n  AND created_by = :user_id\n  AND status != 'process'
activate DB

DB --> ProjectSvc: 1 row affected
deactivate DB

ProjectSvc --> UI: 200 OK\n{\n  "message": "Project deleted",\n  "deleted_at": "2025-12-21T10:30:00Z"\n}
deactivate ProjectSvc

UI -> UI: Remove project from list\n(fade out animation)

UI -> UI: Show toast notification:\n"Project deleted successfully"

UI --> User: Display updated list\n(without deleted project)
deactivate UI

== Exception: Try to Delete Running Project ==

User -> UI: Click "Delete"\n(on Running project)
activate UI

UI -> UI: Check status = "process"

UI -> UI: Delete button is DISABLED\n(grayed out, unclickable)

note over UI
  Business rule enforced at UI level:
  Running projects cannot be deleted
  to prevent data loss
end note

UI --> User: Button disabled,\ntooltip: "Cannot delete\nrunning projects"
deactivate UI

@enduml
